OL,3,CMan stabbed in both legs following
OL,4,Cassault
OL,6,FA man has suffered stab wounds to both
OL,7,Flegs following an incident in west
OL,8,FBelfast.
OL,10,FIt happened in Lenadoon Avenue area at
OL,11,Faround 3.05am on Saturday.
OL,13,FPolice were called to reports that a
OL,14,Fman was being attacked by a number of
OL,15,Fmales.
OL,17,FThey attended the scene alongside
OL,18,FAmbulance Service and a man was taken
OL,19,Fto hospital for treatment on stab
OL,20,Fwounds to both legs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
