OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779117069
OL,3,CMan stabbed in both legs following
OL,4,Cassault
OL,6,FThree men ` a 42-year-old, 33 and 31-
OL,7,Fyear-old ` were subsequently arrested
OL,8,Fon suspicion of grievous bodily harm
OL,9,Fwith intent.
OL,11,FThey remain in police custody at this
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Our
OL,15,Fenquiries are ongoing and we would
OL,16,Fappeal to anyone who was in the area
OL,17,Fat the time and has any information,
OL,18,Fincluding CCTV, ring-doorbell or other
OL,19,Ffootage, to contact us on the 101
OL,20,Fnumber."
